caption.title: Epidemic curve of chikungunya and dengue cases and vector infestation rates reported in Rio Abajo and Juan Diaz counties from 2014 to July 2015.
caption.p: A. Rio Abajo County B. Juan Diaz County. Red bar represents chikungunya imported cases and green bar autochthonous cases. Grey bar represent dengue cases and line blue represent the infestation index mosquitos (percentage).
